n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0dee3d89c74b328189a0fbd072a8ea5fb6f1cf2b","tid":1853583,"uid":164509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1789df238fed3eedceeb5d9923135f6d549c62d2","tid":1853583,"uid":347309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"點樣一個人買一盒？<br />\n身份證？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:22:45.000Z","msg":"可能送貨地址不重複？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf44df66978c850b98e092041c50922a57178324","tid":1853583,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n誠哥好波"},{"pid":"32b510e2cbc0dd1b4ee05509a8b0f7bd546c37ed","tid":1853583,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1789df238fed3eedceeb5d9923135f6d549c62d2","tid":1853583,"uid":347309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"點樣一個人買一盒？<br />\n身份證？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:27:51.000Z","msg":"手機號碼?<br />\n<br />\n斷估唔會有人咁無聊為左一盒口罩買十幾廿張電話卡掛"},{"pid":"75598142ead222cced6553081dbcb2c0a3142fb6","tid":1853583,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"無關公，食屎啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（旋風腿）"},{"pid":"f24c84b5fcfa316d961d296ac640fb5a3f72afd5","tid":1853583,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b2e2fba1964cd70e0b4d79c00d9b00016d60e35","tid":1853583,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dop2300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdop2300.jpg&h=9538623c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擺明同林鄭對著幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkg